{
  "stem": "617.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you know, we also stopped, like I said, when they were-- because some-- some of them were taken off at Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then it was  Latvia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then it was Estonia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were rushed out, to rush out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were taken by trucks to this camp, which we find out it's called Riga-Kaiserwald.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were-- during the day-- we were there for about three weeks-- during the day, we were taken to the railroad and sort of picking stones and carting stones in the-- in the wheelbarrows.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then at night, they would bring us back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was going on for about three weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't as large camp as Auschwitz, or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But of course, nobody-- everybody was busy looking after themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't much that we thought.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we couldn't think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I think we were stopped and given drugs in our food, because nobody was thinking of anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when we were talking to one another, it was always, oh, when we'll be free, and we'll go home to our homes and to our parents.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "None of us, none of us, believed that this is not going to be that way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That our parents were killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "None of us were thinking of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And because we were so hungry, we would sit and-- and sort of talk about cooking recipes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "How good this was, or how good that would be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I did it-- my parents did it this way, or my mother cooked it that way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This is what we were talking about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not necessarily.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there were-- like I said, there were some mothers and daughters, too, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Younger.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
